---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 339
  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI iii
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Art and Skill in Work
---
One with such a concentrated mind rises above the tumult of the
subjective as well as of the objective world. He is like the
arrow-maker, who while fashioning his arrows is conscious only of his
task.
